text:
Neg.
No. 205

Social Conditions in Manhattan: At the head of the decayed stairway in No. 134 Seventh Ave., shown, lives a family with four little children. The balustrade has fallen away from the wall. Published in the New York Evening World of February 23, 1926.

February 23, 1926.

Gift of New York World.
title: Social Conditions in Manhattan.
